snippet.title: Boxy Kingdom (iOS) Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download FREE on iOS ► https://bitly.com/BoxyIOS

Boxy Kingdom is an endless suspenseful arcade/adventure game of pure survival, exploration and looting. And this free-to-play game opens a golden chest of new of innovations and compelling gameplay features.

Coming Soon to Android.
